value.value: Catalysis of the reaction: sedoheptulose 1,7-bisphosphate + H2O = sedoheptulose 7-phosphate + phosphate.
Catalysis of the reaction: sepiapterin + H2O = xanthopterin-B2 + NH3.
Catalysis of the reaction: 1D-5-O-methyl-myo-inositol + NAD+ = 2D-5-O-methyl-2,3,5/4,6-pentahydroxycyclohexanone + H+ + NADH.
Catalysis of the reaction: L-serine + glyoxylate = 3-hydroxypyruvate + glycine.
Catalysis of the reaction: L-serine + H2O + NAD+ = 3-hydroxypyruvate + NH3 + NADH.
Catalysis of the reaction: L-serine O-sulfate + H2O = pyruvate + NH3 + sulfate.
Catalysis of the reaction: UDP-glucose + sinapate = UDP + 1-sinapoyl-D-glucose.
Catalysis of the reaction: O-sinapoylcholine + H2O = choline + H+ + sinapate.
Catalysis of the reaction: D-glucitol 6-phosphate + H2O = D-glucitol + phosphate.
Catalysis of the reaction: L-sorbose + NADP+ = 5-dehydro-D-fructose + H+ + NADPH.
Catalysis of the reaction: L-sorbose + A = 5-dehydro-D-fructose + AH(2).
Catalysis of the reaction: spermidine + acceptor + H2O = 1,3-diaminopropane + 4-aminobutanal + reduced acceptor.
Catalysis of the reaction: H2O + sphingomyelin = ceramide 1-phosphate + choline + H+.
Catalysis of the reaction: acyl-CoA + sphingosine = CoA + N-acylsphingosine.
Catalysis of the reaction: AH2 + O2 + pregna-4,9(11)-diene-3,20-dione = 9,11alpha-epoxypregn-4-ene-3,20-dione + A + H2O.
Catalysis of the reaction: H2O + testololactone = H+ + testolate.
Catalysis of the reaction: 3'-phosphoadenosine 5'-phosphosulfate + a phenolic steroid = adenosine 3',5'-bisphosphate + steroid O-sulfate.
Catalysis of the reaction: cholesteryl-beta-D-glucoside + H2O = D-glucose + cholesterol.
Catalysis of the reaction: H2O + stipitatonate = CO2 + H+ + stipitatate.
Catalysis of the reaction: L-dopa + O2 = 4-(L-alanin-3-yl)-2-hydroxy-cis,cis-muconate 6-semialdehyde + H+.
Catalysis of the reaction: 3,4-dihydroxy-L-phenylalanine + O2 = 5-(L-alanin-3-yl)-2-hydroxy-cis,cis-muconate 6-semialdehyde.
Catalysis of the reaction: ATP + streptomycin = ADP + 2 H+ + streptomycin 3''-phosphate.
Catalysis of the reaction: ATP + streptomycin = ADP + 2 H+ + streptomycin 6-phosphate.
Catalysis of the reaction: H2O + streptomycin 6-phosphate = phosphate + streptomycin.
Catalysis of the reaction: H2O + indole-3-acetaldehyde + O2 = (indol-3-yl)acetate + H+ + H2O2.
Catalysis of the reaction: H2O + NAD+ + L-lysine = NH3 + NADH + allysine.

definition.value: Note that this term has a MetaCyc pathway reference as the pathway only has a single step.

value.value: Catalysis of the reaction: H2O + 2 cytochrome c + nitrogen = 2 reduced cytochrome c + nitrous oxide.
Catalysis of the reaction: N-(carboxymethyl)-D-alanine + H2O + NAD+ = glycine + H+ + NADH + pyruvate.
Catalysis of the reaction: 2 sucrose = D-glucose + 1F-beta-D-fructosylsucrose.
Catalysis of the reaction: sucrose 6F-phosphate + H2O = sucrose + phosphate.
Catalysis of the reaction: sugar phosphate + H2O = sugar + phosphate.
Catalysis of the reaction: H2O + sugar phosphorylated on the terminal carbon = a sugar + phosphate.
Catalysis of the reaction: sulfite + 2 ferricytochrome c + H2O = sulfate + 2 ferrocytochrome c.
Catalysis of the reaction: hydrogen sulfide + 3 oxidized ferredoxin + 3 H2O = sulfite + 3 reduced ferredoxin.
Catalysis of the reaction: S-sulfanylglutathione + O2 + H2O = sulfite + glutathione + 2 H+.
Catalysis of the reaction: 1,3-diaminopropane + S-adenosylmethioninamine = S-methyl-5'-thioadenosine + bis(3-aminopropyl)amine + H+.
Catalysis of the reaction: synephrine = (4-hydroxyphenyl)acetaldehyde + methylammonium.
Catalysis of the reactions: ATP + dGMP = ADP + dGDP, and ATP + dTMP = ADP + dTDP.
Catalysis of the reaction: D-tagatose + ATP = D-tagatose 6-phosphate + ADP + 2 H+.
Catalysis of the reaction: digallate + H2O = 2 gallate + H+.
Catalysis of the reaction: L-tartrate + H+ = D-glycerate + CO2.
Catalysis of the reaction: L-tartrate = (2R,3S)-tartrate.
Catalysis of the reaction: ATP + tau-protein = ADP + O-phospho-tau-protein.
Catalysis of the reaction: taurine + 2-oxoglutarate = sulfoacetaldehyde + L-glutamate.
Catalysis of the reaction: A + H2O + taurine = AH(2) + NH4 + sulfoacetaldehyde.
Catalysis of the reaction: ATP + taurocyamine = N-phosphotaurocyamine + ADP + 2 H+.
Catalysis of the reaction: H2O + NAD+ + tauropine = H+ + NADH + pyruvate + taurine.
Catalysis of the reaction: taxifolin + NAD(P)H + H+ + O2 = 2,3-dihydrogossypetin + NAD(P)+ + H2O.
Catalysis of the reaction: (S)-tetrahydroberberine + 2 O2 = berberine + 2 H2O2.
Catalysis of the reaction: tetrahydroxypteridine = H+ + xanthine-8-carboxylate.
